{"tid":153442,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"第一次去日本，應該去邊先好？","createTime":"2017-03-12T14:51:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-12T16:13:56.000Z","uid":82602,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0fc21efc0c61573298e025e062d6632d424030b5","tid":153442,"uid":82602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T14:51:02.000Z","msg":"如題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講埋點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9796575061a73093fa0bf1dc6913b3e7937318be","tid":153442,"uid":31962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T14:52:00.000Z","msg":"東京 乜都唔駛諗 方便"},{"pid":"c2e9f8f425099e921fad701f20ec7c2de499a124","tid":153442,"uid":73311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T14:53:58.000Z","msg":"大阪京都<br />\n有得買有得睇<br />\n東京真係買買買同買!"},{"pid":"5224a4f60814812093c4cdc382d97fedca1620c1","tid":153442,"uid":82602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T15:00:00.000Z","msg":"可唔可以share埋經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大阪東京都有諗過 但唔想去啲遊客集中區<br />\n有冇人可以share下福岡果頭有咩玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e3e155d22086e3b2ccf8834d08f0a9ee7c2db69","tid":153442,"uid":51148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T15:16:41.000Z","msg":"大阪啦 又近京都"},{"pid":"84a808d4199b4d59477c6602327b8b558c371b0f","tid":153442,"uid":34692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T15:38:24.000Z","msg":"其實你有啲矛盾<br />\n因為大城市交通方便，適合新手<br />\n不過同時有好多遊客<br />\n郊區就正正相反<br />\n咁你想揀邊樣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d78eee1082878babcc7c227947b89cdc059258c0","tid":153442,"uid":11779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T15:48:11.000Z","msg":"沖繩 去到機場join local tour就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28d28ee423896b655792c41e7583cf9d8ac79ba5","tid":153442,"uid":73064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T15:52:32.000Z","msg":"第一次去左東京+大阪10日<br />\n冇planning,就咁買左張7日pass同關西3日pass,每朝早先再諗去邊度玩。<br />\n還掂都未去過，就鳩遊下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n樓主可以試下買pass由東京搭新幹線去金澤，再轉jr落大阪，6個半鍾度，幾好既體驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n淨係睇女都值回票價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d3f8d423bc38445b8010564d7a119884e66bc86","tid":153442,"uid":40171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T15:54:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可唔可以share埋經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大阪東京都有諗過 但唔想去啲遊客集中區<br />\n有冇人可以share下福岡果頭有咩玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就算係東京大阪都有大把多當地人 遊客唔多嘅地方<br />\n福岡都有多遊客嘅地方<br />\n<br />\n我自己都係去咗幾次自由行先開始識得搵唔多遊客又值得去嘅地方"},{"pid":"c941ecb65ae8b5ebe1e935e8e2fb561699981ca2","tid":153442,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T15:57:35.000Z","msg":"福島"},{"pid":"8da47f1bceeb5a74687582e5400d4a0f640ef870","tid":153442,"uid":49868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"